Using bucket sort- 
Example
s = "tree"

Frequency map:
t -> 1
r -> 1
e -> 2

Create buckets:
index = frequency
bucket[0] = {}
bucket[1] = {t, r}
bucket[2] = {e}
bucket[3] = {}
bucket[4] = {}

Now traverse buckets from high frequency to low:
2 -> e
1 -> t, r

Answer:
eert



